{"type": "article", "id": 3710, "title": "艺术家做的Adidas Originals", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-20T07:43:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233209AOKoNt9PmF5dD60z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t洛杉矶艺术馆 HVW8 日前正在举行由两位美国街头艺术家 Kevin Lyons 与 Jean André 携手设计的 「Adidas Originals 」主题展览。两人以阿迪达斯的两款经典鞋款 Seeley 与 Adi-Ease 为蓝本，在其鞋面上进行创作。在 Adi-Ease 款众，色彩斑斓的涂鸦艺术跃然鞋面，像是不经意间打翻了调色盘似的随性，又带有强烈的波普艺术风格。而另一款则选用了黑白色系的主色调，给人一种穿着纯白色的球鞋从黑墨水池中走出的感觉一般，Jean André 只眼一双耐看又耐穿且设计独特的鞋子才是他最喜欢的。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233205Xvag01UQFWzMIOy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233206sP9pvYGKalATZoE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233206vEHDjKxWL0UhI4Pl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233207gm86EBPXq2MvhyNY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233207PsN5rTEUwdvZC2SQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}